{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Cool thing Thursday: Fog of World","content":"<a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/area-explored.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5366\" title=\"Area of world explored\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/area-explored.png\" alt=\"Area of world explored\" width=\"507\" height=\"68\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/area-explored.png 507w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/area-explored-300x40.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/percentage-explored.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5367\" title=\"Percentage of world explored\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/percentage-explored.png\" alt=\"Percentage of world explored\" width=\"506\" height=\"70\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/percentage-explored.png 506w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/percentage-explored-300x41.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></a>\n<p><a href=\"http://fogofworld.com\" target=\"_blank\">Fog of World</a> is a toy.</p>\n<p>A wonderful magnificent toy I wouldn&#8217;t let you pry from my cold dead fingers! And I wish it came out six months ago, not last week.</p>\n<p>What is it?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5368\" style=\"width: 317px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ljubljana-fog.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5368  \" title=\"Fog over my world\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ljubljana-fog.png\" alt=\"Fog over my world\" width=\"307\" height=\"461\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ljubljana-fog.png 640w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/ljubljana-fog-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 307px) 100vw, 307px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fog over my world</p></div>\n<p>Oh it&#8217;s just an <em>awesome</em>Â visualisation of where you&#8217;ve been in your life and how much of the world you&#8217;ve explored so far. That runs on your <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"iPhone\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/iphone\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone</a>. And sucks the ever living hell out of your battery with the GPS chip.</p>\n<p>To be honest, I&#8217;m not even certain why I like it. Probably the same reason I like <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Foursquare\" href=\"http://www.foursquare.com/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\">Foursquare</a> &#8230; it&#8217;s just incredibly cool to have a historical log of where you&#8217;ve been and what you&#8217;ve been up to. Call me sentimental, but that&#8217;s really cool. Even though I find looking at old photographs boring, a log of locations? Sold.</p>\n<p>Maybe I&#8217;m just a traveler at heart.</p>\n<p>The more important aspect of Fog of World is that it affects your life ever so imperceptibly. Walking around town yesterday &#8211; less than a kilometer from home &#8211; I discovered a new street. Just because I wanted to expand my fog of world a bit, get that tiny small percentage more. Explore just a bit.</p>\n<p>It was marvelous. I love it when software gently nudges me to expand my horizons.</p>\n<p>That said, this has been a marvelous year for traveling. I&#8217;ve been to <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"London\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=51.5072222222,-0.1275&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=51.5072222222,-0.1275 (London)&amp;t=h\" rel=\"geolocation\" target=\"_blank\">London</a>, <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Novi Sad\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=45.25,19.85&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=45.25,19.85 (Novi%20Sad)&amp;t=h\" rel=\"geolocation\" target=\"_blank\">Novi Sad</a>, <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Belgrade\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=44.8205555556,20.4622222222&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=44.8205555556,20.4622222222 (Belgrade)&amp;t=h\" rel=\"geolocation\" target=\"_blank\">Belgrade</a>, <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Old City of Dubrovnik\" href=\"http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/95\" rel=\"unesco\" target=\"_blank\">Dubrovnik</a>, <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Zurich\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=47.3666666667,8.55&amp;spn=0.1,0.1&amp;q=47.3666666667,8.55 (Zurich)&amp;t=h\" rel=\"geolocation\" target=\"_blank\">Zurich</a> and I&#8217;m going to Paris in a week. If only this app existed 6 months earlier, there would be much less fog over my world.</p>\n<p>But hey, just discovered I can import all my <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"RunKeeper\" href=\"http://www.runkeeper.com/\" rel=\"homepage\" target=\"_blank\">RunKeeper</a> data going back to early 2011. Sweet!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5371\" style=\"width: 416px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/downtown-ljubljana-fog.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5371 \" title=\"Downtown perambulations are quite sporadic\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/downtown-ljubljana-fog.png\" alt=\"Downtown perambulations are quite sporadic\" width=\"406\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/downtown-ljubljana-fog.png 508w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/downtown-ljubljana-fog-203x300.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 406px) 100vw, 406px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Downtown perambulations are quite sporadic</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5372\" style=\"width: 394px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/photo-3.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5372 \" title=\"The app eggs you on to travel more\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/photo-3.png\" alt=\"The app eggs you on to travel more\" width=\"384\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/photo-3.png 640w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/photo-3-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 384px) 100vw, 384px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">The app eggs you on to travel more</p></div>\n<h6 class=\"zemanta-related-title\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">Related articles</h6>\n<ul class=\"zemanta-article-ul zemanta-article-ul-image\" style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"padding: 0; background: none; list-style: none; display: block; float: left; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; width: 84px; font-size: 11px; margin: 2px 10px 10px 2px;\"><a style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #999; padding: 2px; display: block; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.gizmodo.co.uk/2012/10/this-fog-of-world-app-might-be-the-funnest-app-ive-seen-in-a-long-time/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; width: 80px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://i.zemanta.com/116068823_80_80.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a style=\"display: block; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; line-height: 12pt; height: 80px; padding: 5px 2px 0 2px;\" href=\"http://www.gizmodo.co.uk/2012/10/this-fog-of-world-app-might-be-the-funnest-app-ive-seen-in-a-long-time/\" target=\"_blank\">This Fog of World App Might Be the Funnest App I&#8217;ve Seen in a Long Time</a></li>\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"padding: 0; background: none; list-style: none; display: block; float: left; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; width: 84px; font-size: 11px; margin: 2px 10px 10px 2px;\"><a style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #999; padding: 2px; display: block; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.ocregister.com/news/inland-373439-weather-highs.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; width: 80px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://i.zemanta.com/116196619_80_80.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a style=\"display: block; overflow: 